text: Investing in affordable housing is about giving everyone a real & fair chance at success. Today we announced a historic investment in @TOHousing, so almost 60,000 families here can have safe, comfortable, and affordable places to call home: https://bit.ly/2s7HnhC pic.twitter.com/WnA7rPvT0Q

Débile.https://twitter.com/GinettePT/status/1113554876372520965 …

After @cathmckenna lies about CO2 being pollution and carbon tax making us richer, here we have Canada’s Health min telling us we’re going to have heart attacks, diabetes and mental problems because climate is changing. Nuts.https://twitter.com/GinettePT/status/1113556227957645313 …

Last week I spoke with leading scientists about Canada’s Changing Climate Report. Canada is warming at 2x the global average. We need to act now so our kids can have a healthy planet & good jobs. A price on pollution is a key part of that. Read the report: https://bit.ly/2FJgreZ pic.twitter.com/8uEnfrPRAn

La semaine passée j’ai parlé avec des scientifiques du Rapport sur le climat changeant du Canada. Le Canada se réchauffe 2x plus vite que la moyenne mondiale. On doit agir pour nos enfants, et c’est en tarifiant la pollution qu’on va y arriver. Le rapport: https://bit.ly/2COwYxG pic.twitter.com/CRyUEPqNnO

Justin Trudeau has been trying to mislead Canadians for months. But this time he got caught. His story yesterday doesn’t match all his previous excuses. It turns out if you tell the truth, there’s is no room for you in the Liberal Party of Canada.pic.twitter.com/QdDJZ3godt

Justin Trudeau tente de tromper les Canadiens depuis des mois. Mais cette fois il s’est fait prendre. Sa version d’hier ne correspond pas à toutes ses excuses précédentes. Il semble que si vous dites la vérité, il n’y a pas de place pour vous au Parti libéral du Canada.pic.twitter.com/cjVE84oXDB
